name: Unidentified_Kaleesh_chieftain
content:
During her travels, the Jedi Master Yuon Par became blood sister to a chieftain of the Kaleesh species sometime before the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.
The Kaleesh chieftain was mentioned in the Codex entry for Yuon Par in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011.
